snippet.title: Stranger Things 5 | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
Every battle has led to this.

More about Stranger Things 5:
The fall of 1987. Hawkins is scarred by the opening of the Rifts, and our heroes are united by a single goal: find and kill Vecna. But he has vanished — his whereabouts and plans unknown. Complicating their mission, the government has placed the town under military quarantine and intensified its hunt for Eleven, forcing her back into hiding. As the anniversary of Will’s disappearance approaches, so does a heavy, familiar dread. The final battle is looming — and with it, a darkness more powerful and more deadly than anything they’ve faced before. To end this nightmare, they’ll need everyone — the full party — standing together, one last time.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81297917

Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films’ Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story…and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question…do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

snippet.title: Titanic 2 (2026) – First Trailer | Leonardo DiCaprio,  Kate Winslet Reunited | Concept Trailer
snippet.description:
#titanic #leonardo #kate 
Watch this “Titanic 2 (2026) – First Trailer | Leonardo DiCaprio & Kate Winslet Reunited | Concept Trailer”

A flood of love and legacy returns.

In this imaginative fan-made concept trailer, Leonardo DiCaprio and Kate Winslet reunite decades after their iconic voyage aboard the Titanic. Now as older versions of Jack and Rose—or perhaps their children—they navigate love, loss, and destiny under the specter of the legendary ship.

Set against breathtaking ocean vistas and emotional reunions, Titanic 2 explores the echoes of the past and the bonds that transcend time. Expect sweeping romance, haunting visuals, and a journey between memory and hope.

snippet.title: Piya Ghar Aaya - Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan (Asad's Remix)
snippet.description:
All praise to Ustaad Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan.

I'm excited to finally share the full version. Thanks for waiting so patiently (most of you :p)
I'm starting off my new series called EIGHT x EIGHT with this track, As a part of this series I'll put out a new song every Thursday for the next 8 weeks

I grew up in Pakistan, and I now live in Canada. My family is from Faisalabad. Growing up, my grandfather listened to a lot of qawwali around me as a kid and that influence never left my dna. After years of making music, I finally did something with a track from Ustaad Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan. I also really enjoyed seeing videos of this track from all over the world, specially from home - thank you for sharing those. 

This remix blew up on TikTok, Instagram etc but more importantly, as you can see in this video, it created a beautiful moment for a group of people and that's what music is all about. Ustaad Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan's legacy continues to serve moments like this, I'm grateful to have been a vessel. 

Thanks for showing this so much love, lots more music soon

Asad 
-
Download in High Quality: https://asadkhanlife.bandcamp.com/track/piya-ghar-aaya-asads-remix
More music + Socials: https://tr.ee/4Hvf7x

snippet.title: Predator: Badlands | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
First hunt. Last chance.

From the director of Prey, watch the brand-new trailer for Predator: Badlands, in theaters November 7.

“Predator: Badlands,” which stars Elle Fanning and Dimitrius Schuster-Koloamatangi, is set in the future on a remote planet, where a young Predator, outcast from his clan, finds an unlikely ally in Thia (Fanning) and embarks on a treacherous journey in search of the ultimate adversary. The film is directed by Dan Trachtenberg and produced by John Davis, Dan Trachtenberg, Marc Toberoff, Ben Rosenblatt, Brent O’Connor.

snippet.title: Ali Hi Haq Tha (Banaam-e-Haidar 3) | Muhammad Samie | Official Video
snippet.description:
CREDITS:
Singer: Muhammad Samie
Poet: Muhammad Samie
Composer: Muhammad Samie
===========================
AUDIO CREW:
Music Production: Jay Ali
Music Direction: Muhammad Samie & Jay Ali
Main Harmonium: Muhammad Samie
Second Harmonium: Jay Ali
Tabla: Irfan Aly
Dholak: Irfan Aly & Kamran Ali
Mandolin & Guitars: Mumtaz Hussain
Chorus Vocals: Ali Hassan, Ali Murtaza & Arslan Ali
Recording: Jay Ali
Mixing & Mastering: Jay Ali
===========================
VIDEO CREW:
Director: Muhammad Samie
Video Concept: Muhammad Samie & Suleman Shah
Cinematographer: Suleman Shah
DOP: Suleman Shah
Gaffer: Usman Rizwan
Art Work: Muhammad Samie
Wardrobe: Muhammad Samie
Lighting Production: Light & Grip Productions
Post-Production: Suleman Shah
Production House: Kul Andar Films

A Presentation by Short Sufi Films
============
LYRICS:
Ali hi haq tha Ali hi haq hai Ali ki naslon mein haq rahe ga
Ali viraasat hai Mustafa ki, Ali hi mash’hood-e-haq rahe ga

Tu wo walad hai jo lam-yalid ke makaan se jalwa-numa hua hai
Tu nashir-e-dawa-e-salooni, tu kya hai? Sab ko guman hua hai
Tu qasim-e-noor-e-Mustafa hai, tu nafs-e-Payghambar-e-Khuda hai
Tu markaz-e-Awliya-e-alam, tu bil-yaqeen fakhr-e-Ambiya hai

Ali mizaaj-e-Muhammadi hai, Ali to asrar-e-haq rahe ga
Ali hi haq tha Ali hi haq hai Ali ki naslon mein haq rahe ga

Tu hi Risaalat ki hai khilafat, tu hi wilayat tu hi imamat
Tu kurra-e-arz-e-Kibriya pe Nabi ki hai awaleen shahadat
Tu mehvar-e-ilm-e-do-sara hai, tu kashif-e-maqsad-e-ibadat
Tu hai siraat-e-nijaat-e-insaan, hai qalb-e-momin teri riyasat

Tumhara rahbar tumhain mubarak, hamara rahbar Ali rahe ga
Ali hi haq tha Ali hi haq hai Ali ki naslon mein haq rahe ga

Wo badr ho ya mubahila ho, ya phir Muhammad ki wo kisaa ho
Wo chahe Marhab ka samna ho, ya phir wo khandaq ka ma’rka ho
Uhud mein dhaal-e-Payambari ya, buton ka Ka’be se khaatma ho
Ya wo wilayat ki taaj-poshi ba-dast-e-at'haar-e-Mustafa ho

Ali se daman bachane wale, Ali tujhe jaa ba jaa mile ga
Ali hi haq tha Ali hi haq hai Ali ki naslon mein haq rahe ga

Nabi ke deen ki ragon mein Haider lahu ki soorat ravaan rahe ga
Ali ka munkir zaleel-o-ruswa azal se tha hashr tak rahe ga
Ali hi haq tha Ali hi haq hai Ali ki naslon mein haq rahe ga

Bus Ali Ali Bus Ali Ali ...

Aao ji Ali Ali wird paka laiyay
Ghaman nu chadd aj khushiyan mana laiyay
Ral ke aakhiye, “Baad Muhammad
Sab ton afzal zikr-e-Ali" Bus

Ali Ali Bus Ali Ali Bus ...

Ali de chehre nu takna ibadat
Ali da naan loko japna ibadat
Ki ki mein dassan tenu sifat Ali di
Jane Ali nu Khuda Ya Nabi bus

Ali Ali Bus Ali Ali Bus ...

Haider, safdar, sher-e-ghazanfar
Rahbar-e-akbar, mard-e-muzaffar
At'har, azhar, Haq da mazhar
Peeng de andar cheereya azdar
Deen da anbar, Khvaja Qambar
Veer Paighambar, awwal number
Baad Muhammad sab ton bartar
Ikko baan nal puteya Khyber
Ilm samandar, fakhr-e-Sikandar
Mard-e-Qalandar, loon loon andar
Badr ton lay ke Khandak, Khyber
Dushman cheer ke langeya Haider
Tayyab, tahir, banda-parwar
Rooh-e-munawwar, maula, sarwar
Hadi, mahdi, aali-gauhar
Zahra paak da suchha shauhar
Qazi-e-azam, alim-e-alam
Shams-e-wilayat, Noor-e-hidayat
Aashiq Rab da, Paak nasab da
Ghaiz ghazab da, Hunar kasab da
Mahir sab da, Fakhr Arab da
Baap Hassan da, Phol chaman da
Raah adan da, shah zaman da 
Waar Ali da, kair Khuda da
Ishq Ali da, lutf Khuda da
Bol Ali de, hukam Khuda da
Deed Ali di, karam Khuda da

Bus Ali Ali Bus Ali Ali Bus ...

#muhammadsamie #shortsufispells #qawwali

snippet.title: मॉर्टल कॉमबैट II (Mortal Kombat II) - Official Hindi Trailer
snippet.description:
इसे कहते है मॉर्टल कॉमबैट (II). देखिये 'मॉर्टल कॉमबैट II' का हिंदी ट्रेलर, जल्द आ रही है आपके नज़दीकी सिनेमाघरों में अक्टूबर २४, २०२५ से। In English, Hindi, Tamil & Telugu. Also in IMAX. #MortalKombatMovie

Website: www.warnerbros-india.com
Facebook:   / warnerbrosindia  
Instagram:   / warnerbrosindia  
X: https://x.com/WarnerBrosIndia 

From New Line Cinema comes the latest high-stakes installment in the blockbuster video game franchise in all its brutal glory, Mortal Kombat II.  This time, the fan favorite champions—now joined by Johnny Cage himself—are pitted against one another in the ultimate, no-holds barred, gory battle to defeat the dark rule of Shao Kahn that threatens the very existence of the Earthrealm and its defenders.

Karl Urban stars as Johnny Cage, alongside Adeline Rudolph, Jessica McNamee, Josh Lawson, Ludi Lin, Mehcad Brooks, Tati Gabrielle, Lewis Tan, Damon Herriman, with Chin Han, Tadanobu Asano as Lord Raiden, Joe Taslim as Bi-Han, and Hiroyuki Sanada as Hanzo Hasashi and Scorpion.

Director Simon McQuoid returns to helm the follow up to his explosive 2021 cinematic adventure, from a screenplay by Jeremy Slater, based on the videogame created by Ed Boon and John Tobias.  The film is produced by Todd Garner, James Wan, Toby Emmerich, E. Bennett Walsh and McQuoid, and executive produced by Michael Clear, Judson Scott, Slater and Lawrence Kasanoff.  

Joining McQuoid behind the camera are director of photography Stephen F. Windon, production designer Yohei Taneda, editor Stuart Levy and costume designer Cappi Ireland, with casting by Rich Delia and music by Benjamin Wallfisch.

New Line Cinema Presents an Atomic Monster/Broken Road Production, a Fireside Films Production, Mortal Kombat II. The film will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures, & will release in Cinemas and IMAX® in India on October 24, 2025.

#WarnerBrosIndia #MortalKombatMovieHindiTrailer

snippet.title: WAR 2 Trailer Review ⋮ Looks Big… Feels Flat
snippet.description:
War 2’s trailer is definitely an upgrade from the teaser, offering some narrative intrigue and character stakes — especially with Kabir going rogue and Jr. NTR hunting him down. But the generic action, weak VFX, and over-the-top spectacle kill the excitement, leaving behind a flashy yet emotionally flat experience. #War2 #PJExplained #thePJ

snippet.title: Five Nights at Freddy's 2 | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
We’re not done with you. #FNAF2movie in theaters December 5.

--

They’re not just at Freddy’s anymore. 
 
In 2023, Blumhouse’s box-office horror phenomenon Five Nights at Freddy’s, based on the blockbuster game series by Scott Cawthon, became the highest-grossing horror film of the year. Now, a shocking new chapter of animatronic terror begins. 
 
One year has passed since the supernatural nightmare at Freddy Fazbear’s Pizza. The stories about what transpired there have been twisted into a campy local legend, inspiring the town’s first ever Fazfest. 
 
Former security guard Mike (Josh Hutcherson) and police officer Vanessa (Elizabeth Lail) have kept the truth from Mike’s 11-year-old sister, Abby (Piper Rubio), concerning the fate of her animatronic friends. 
 
But when Abby sneaks out to reconnect with Freddy, Bonnie, Chica, and Foxy, it will set into motion a terrifying series of events, revealing dark secrets about the true origin of Freddy’s, and unleashing a long-forgotten horror hidden away for decades.
 
The cast of Five Nights at Freddy’s 2 includes returning co-stars Theodus Crane as Jeremiah and the legendary Matthew Lillard as William Afton. The film features new characters played by Freddy Carter (Shadow and Bone, Pennyworth), Wayne Knight (Jurassic Park, Seinfeld), Mckenna Grace (Ghostbusters franchise, Annabelle Comes Home) and horror icon Skeet Ulrich (Scream, Riverdale). 
 
Five Nights at Freddy’s 2 is directed by acclaimed returning filmmaker Emma Tammi and is written by game series creator Scott Cawthon.
 
The film is produced by Blumhouse founder and CEO Jason Blum and Scott Cawthon, who together produced the first film. The executive producers are director Emma Tammi, Beatriz Sequeira, Christopher Warner, Russell Binder and Marc Mostman. 
 
The first Freddy’s film opened to a record-shattering $80 million in October 2023 and went on to earn almost $300 million worldwide.
